<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Pesanan Layanan Baru</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset Styles */
        body,
        p,
        h1,
        h2,
        h3,
        h4,
        h5,
        h6 {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f5;
            /* Background luar terang */
            color: #09090b;
            /* Teks gelap */
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        }

        /* Container */
        .email-wrapper {
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #f4f4f5;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }

        .email-card {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            /* Background dalam putih */
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 25px rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.08);
            /* Glow merah tipis */
            border: 1px solid #e4e4e7;
        }

        /* Header */
        .header {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e4e4e7;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            color: #ef4444;
            /* Accent 2 (Merah) */
        }

        .header p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #71717a;
            /* Subtle text */
        }

        /* Body */
        .body-content {
            padding: 30px;
        }

        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #09090b;
        }

        .intro-text {
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #52525b;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        /* Detail Box */
        .details-box {
            background-color: #fafafa;
            border: 1px solid #e4e4e7;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .detail-row {
            display: table;
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .detail-row:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        .detail-label {
            display: table-cell;
            width: 40%;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #52525b;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .detail-value {
            display: table-cell;
            width: 60%;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #09090b;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: right;
        }

        /* Highlight Schedule */
        .schedule-highlight {
            background-color: #fef2f2;
            /* Latar merah sangat muda */
            color: #dc2626;
            /* Accent 1 */
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border: 1px dashed #fca5a5;
        }

        /* Button */
        .btn-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 35px 0 20px 0;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #dc2626;
            /* Accent 1 */
            color: #ffffff !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.25);
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #b91c1c;
        }

        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #a1a1aa;
            background-color: #fafafa;
            border-top: 1px solid #e4e4e7;
        }

        .footer p {
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-wrapper {
                padding: 20px 10px;
            }

            .body-content {
                padding: 20px;
            }

            .detail-label,
            .detail-value {
                display: block;
                width: 100%;
                text-align: left;
            }

            .detail-value {
                margin-top: 4px;
                margin-bottom: 12px;
            }

            .detail-row:last-child .detail-value {
                margin-bottom: 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <table class="email-card" width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
            <!-- Header -->
            <tr>
                <td class="header">
                    <h1>📅 Pesanan Layanan Baru!</h1>
                    <p>Segera persiapkan layanan Anda</p>
                </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- Body -->
            <tr>
                <td class="body-content">
                    <p class="greeting">Halo {{OwnerName}},</p>
                    <p class="intro-text">
                        Kabar baik! Ada pesanan layanan baru yang masuk untuk outlet <strong>{{OutletName}}</strong>.
                        Berikut adalah rincian pesanan yang perlu Anda ketahui:
                    </p>

                    <!-- Highlight Jadwal -->
                    <div class="schedule-highlight">
                        Jadwal: {{BookingDate}} | Pukul {{BookingTime}}
                    </div>

                    <!-- Detail Pesanan -->
                    <div class="details-box">
                        <div class="detail-row">
                            <span class="detail-label">ID Pesanan</span>
                            <span class="detail-value">#{{OrderId}}</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="detail-row">
                            <span class="detail-label">Layanan</span>
                            <span class="detail-value">{{ServiceName}}</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="detail-row">
                            <span class="detail-label">Pelanggan</span>
                            <span class="detail-value">{{CustomerName}}</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="detail-row">
                            <span class="detail-label">Kontak</span>
                            <span class="detail-value">{{CustomerPhone}}</span>
                        </div>
                        <!-- Tambahan Metode Pembayaran -->
                        <div class="detail-row">
                            <span class="detail-label">Metode Pembayaran</span>
                            <span class="detail-value">{{PaymentMethod}}</span>
                        </div>
                        <!-- Tambahan Nama Kasir -->
                        <div class="detail-row">
                            <span class="detail-label">Diproses Oleh (Kasir)</span>
                            <span class="detail-value">{{StaffName}}</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="detail-row">
                            <span class="detail-label">Total Pembayaran</span>
                            <!-- Menggunakan warna accent3 (Orange) seperti yang direquest sebelumnya -->
                            <span class="detail-value" style="color: #ea580c;">Rp {{TotalAmount}}</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="detail-row">
                            <span class="detail-label">Status</span>
                            <span class="detail-value">{{PaymentStatus}}</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <p class="intro-text" style="margin-bottom: 0; font-size: 14px;">
                        Silakan cek dashboard aplikasi untuk melihat detail lebih lengkap atau mengelola pesanan ini.
                    </p>
                </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- Footer -->
            <tr>
                <td class="footer">
                    <p>Email ini dihasilkan secara otomatis. Mohon tidak membalas email ini.</p>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </div>
</body>

</html>